<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nesil-caliskan> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Nesil Caliskan was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government on 12 May 2026. She was previously Comptroller of HM Household (Government Whip) from 7 September 2025 to 12 May 2026. She was elected as the MP for Barking in July 2024."@en .
